(225, 2, 'If target has a berry, inflicts double damage and uses the berry.', 'Inflicts [regular damage]{mechanic:regular-damage}.  If the target is holding a berry, this move has double power, and the user takes the berry and uses it immediately.\n\nIf the target is holding a []{item:jaboca-berry} or []{item:rowap-berry}, the berry is still removed, but has no effect.\n\nIf this move is [super effective]{mechanic:super-effective} and the target is holding a berry that can reduce this move''s damage, it will do so, and will not be stolen.'),
(225, 3, 'If target has a berry, inflicts double damage and uses the berry.', 'Inflicts [regular damage]{mechanic:regular-damage}.  If the target is holding a berry, this move has double power, and the user takes the berry and uses it immediately.\n\nIf the target is holding a []{item:jaboca-berry} or []{item:rowap-berry}, the berry is still removed, but has no effect.\n\nIf this move is [super effective]{mechanic:super-effective} and the target is holding a berry that can reduce this move''s damage, it will do so, and will not be stolen.'),
